snippet.title: Mirai Trailer Telugu | Teja Sajja | Manchu Manoj | Karthik Gattamneni | PMF | 12th Sept
snippet.description:
Presenting the most awaited #MiraiTrailer Telugu!!

#Mirai is an upcoming Indian action-adventure film starring  #TejaSajja, #ManchuManoj, Ritika Nayak & Others. Directed by Karthik Gattamneni. Produced by TG Vishwa Prasad and Krithi Prasad under People Media Factory. 

In Cinemas 12th September, 2025 Worldwide.

Cast: Super Hero Teja Sajja, Manoj Manchu, Ritika Nayak, Shriya Saran, Jayaram, Jagapathi Babu

Crew: 
Director – Karthik Gattamneni
 Producers – T.G. Vishwa Prasad, Krithi Prasad
 Written By – Karthik Gattamneni, Manibabu Karanam
 Editor – Sreekar Prasad
 Music – Gowra Hari
 Director of Photography (DOP) – Karthik Gattamneni
 Dialogues – Manibabu Karanam
 CEP – Sujith Kumar Kolli
 Production Designer – Srinagendra Tangala
 Co-Director – Anil Anand
 Associate Producer – Gautam Reddy
 Action Choreography – Pradeet Seelum (Nung), Kecha Khampakdee, Maibam Nabakanta, Real Satish, Rabin Subbu, Stunts Jaswa, Stunts Sri, Nandu, Amrit Singh, Kishore Verma
 VFX Supervisor – Ramji Dott
 Production Controller – Korrapati Venkata Ramana
 Costume Designers – Rekha Boggarapu, Lanka Santoshi (for Teja Sajja)
 Art Director – Dasireddy Srinivas (Pandu)
 Chief Associate Editor – Uthura
 VFX Co-ordinator – Rajesh Muthu Subbaiah
 Color by – Deccan Dreams, Colorist – S.B. Yugendhran
 VFX by – PMF VFX, Deccan Dreams
 VFX Head – K. Surya
 VFX Supervisors – Jagan, Kumar Nirmala Srujan
 Sound Design – Raghunath Kemisetty
 Dolby Atmos Mix – E. Radha Krishna D.F. Tech
 Lyrics – Chandrabose, KK Balaji, Manibabu Karanam
 Choreographer – Polaki Vijay
 Chief Associate Directors – Kiran Bejjanki, Uthura
 Associate Directors – Shyaam Gaikwad, Abhiram Pamarthi, Manoj Duggireddy
 Associate Directors – Pareena S. Acharya, Likhith Giri Palle, Ashok Prakhyath, Rajath Saini, Somanth Lepakshi, Vamsy Garlapti, Chirayu Paudel, Ganesh Konamarthi, Saikiran Mandapuri
 Operative/Second Unit DOP – Mentem Satheesh
 Cinematography Team – Korlapati Bapiraju, Kora Veerendra Babu, Chandu Vadde, Vinay Ananthu
 Executive Producer – Ram Reddy
 PMF Digital Marketing – Sarath Chandra
 Production Executive – Srinu Chennakesavulu
 Production Manager – Bala
 Asst EP – Kranti Datti, Vineet Sai Kota
 Makeup Chief – I. Srinivas Raju
 Stills – Jagan Setty
 Publicity Designs – Ananth Kancherla, Kabilan Chelliah
 Promos – Kalyan Surya Prakash
 Digital Marketing – Manoj Valluri, Haashtag Media
 PRO – Vamsi Shekar

Trailer theme Music: 
GowraHari 

Keys: 
VikasBadisa 
Siddharth Salur
GowraHari 

Lyrics English & Sanskrit 
GowraHari 

Vocals :
Sai Charan Bhaskaruni
Chaithu Satsangi
Harshavardhan Chavali
Siva Dinavahi
Harini Ivaturi
Sindhuja Srinivasan
Vasa Pavani
Tejaswini Nandibhatla

Children chorus :
Vagdevi
Hamsini
Pradanya

snippet.title: गणपती आरती Ganpati Aarti - सुखकर्ता दुखहर्ता Sukhkarta Dukhharta Full Aarti | Ganpatichi Aarti
snippet.description:
गणपती आरती Ganpati Aarti - सुखकर्ता दुखहर्ता Sukhkarta Dukhharta Full Aarti | Ganpatichi Aarti
गणपती आरती Ganpati Aarti - सुखकर्ता दुखहर्ता Sukhkarta Dukhharta Full Aarti | Ganpatichi Aarti

⭐ मन की शांति के लिए "Vats Bhakti Geet " यूट्यूब चैनल पर भजन और भक्ति गीत,आरती,चालीसा व मंत्र सुने ⭐ Please subscribe to the channel and press Bell icon for all the updates, we are coming up with many new Bhajans  💗﻿🌸

⭐Song : सुखकर्ता दुखहर्ता Sukhkarta Dukhharta
⭐SINGER : Anju Sharma
⭐MUSIC : Gulshan Music
⭐Producer : Gulshan Sharma
⭐Category : Hindi Devotional 
⭐MUSIC LABEL: Vats Bhakti Geet

Lyrics:
Shri Ganpatichi Aarti

Sukhkarta Dukhharta Varta Vighnachi
Nurvi Purvi Prem Krupa Jayachi
Sarvangi Sundar Uti Shendurachi
Kanthi Jhalke Maal Muktaphalanchi
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Mangalmurti
Darshan Maatre Mann Kaamana Poorti
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Ratnakhachit Phara Tujh Gaurikumra
Chandanaachi Uti Kumkum Keshara
Hirejadit Mukut Shobhato Bara
Runjhunati Nupure Charani Ghagariya
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Mangalmurti
Darshan Maatre Mann Kaamana Poorti
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Lambodar Pitambar Phanivar Bandhana
Saral Sond Vakratunda Trinayana
Daas Ramacha Vaat Paahe Sadna
Sankati Pavave Nirvani Rakshave Survarvandana
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Mangalmurti Darshan Matre Mann Kaamana Poorti
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Shri Ganeshachi Aarti

Shendur Laal Chadhayo Achha Gajmukhko
Dondil Laal Biraaje Sut Gauriharko
Haath Liye Gudladdu Sai Survarko
Mahima Kahe Na Jaye Laagat Hun Padko
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Jai Jee Ganaraaj Vidya Sukhdata
Dhanya Tumharo Darshan Mera Mann Ramata
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Ashto Siddhi Daasi Sankatko Bairi
Vighnavinashak Mangal Murat Adhikari
Koti Suraj Prakash Ebi Chhabi Teri
Gandasthalmadmastak Jhule Shashibahari
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Jay Jee Ganaraaj Vidya Sukhdata
Dhanya Tumharo Darshan Mera Mann Ramata
Jai Dev Jai Dev

Bhavbhagat Se Koi Sharnagat Aave
Santat Sampat Sabahi Bharapur Paave
Aise Tum Maharaj Moko Ati Bhave
Gosavinandan Nishidin Gun Gaave
Jai Dev Jai Dev
Jai Jai Jee Ganaraaj Vidya Sukhdata
Dhanya Tumharo Darshan Mera Mann Ramata
Jai Dev Jai Dev

#GanpatiAarti #SukhkartaDukhharta #GanpatiSongs

snippet.title: Baahubali - The Epic Teaser | Prabhas, Rana Daggubati | SS Rajamouli | 31st October 2025
snippet.description:
Baahubali The Epic is a combined narrative of the two-part Indian film saga, weaving together the grandeur and drama of Baahubali: The Beginning and Baahubali: The Conclusion into one epic tale.

CAST

Prabhas as Sivudu & Baahubali, Rana Daggubati as Bhallaladeva, Anushka Shetty as Devasena, Tamannaah as Avanthika with Ramya Krishna, Nasser, Sathyaraj, Kiccha Sudeepa, Adivi Sesh, Rakesh Varre, Meka Ramakrishna.

CREW

Screenplay & Direction: S.S. Rajamouli
Presented by: K. Raghavendra Rao B.A.
Producers: Shobu Yarlagadda & Prasad Devineni
Story: V. Vijayendra Prasad 
DOP: K.K. Senthil Kumar
Production Designer: Sabu Cyril
Music Composer: M.M. Keeravaani
VFX Supervision: V. Srinivas Mohan
Sound Design: P.M. Satheesh
Stunt Choreography: Peter Hein
Additional Stunts: King Solomon, Lee Whittakar, Kaloyan Vodenicharov
Dance Choreographers: Prem Rakshit, Shankar, Dinesh Kumar, Jani

snippet.title: Madharaasi - Official Trailer | Sivakarthikeyan | Rukmini | Vidyut | A.R.Murugadoss | Anirudh
snippet.description:
Junglee Music Tamil drops the much-awaited official trailer of Madharaasi, an action-packed emotional drama written and directed by A.R. Murugadoss. Starring Sivakarthikeyan in a bold, intense role alongside the talented Rukmini Vasanth, the trailer gives a powerful glimpse into a gripping narrative filled with high-stakes moments, strong character arcs, and impactful storytelling. Backed by a compelling background score from Anirudh Ravichander, Madharaasi promises to be a high-voltage entertainer that blends mass appeal with emotional depth.

With stunning visuals, hard-hitting dialogues, and a riveting plot, the Madharaasi trailer has already begun trending among fans of Tamil action movies, Sivakarthikeyan's latest films, and AR Murugadoss' direction. Whether you're here for the sharp screenplay, Anirudh’s electrifying music, or the powerful screen presence of the leads, this is one film that’s gearing up to be a Tamil cinema blockbuster in 2025. Don’t miss out—watch the trailer now and be part of the growing excitement around #MadharaasiTrailer.

#Madharaasi Grand release worldwide on September 5th ❤‍🔥

en-IN.title: 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓 | 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 | 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐡 𝐂𝐡𝐚𝐭𝐮𝐫𝐭𝐡𝐢 𝐒𝐩𝐞𝐜𝐢𝐚𝐥 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 | 𝐕𝐦𝐜 𝐃𝐞𝐯𝐨𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐚𝐥
en-IN.description:
𝐀𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐎 𝐂𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐈𝐓𝐒 :

𝐒𝐎𝐍𝐆 𝐍𝐀𝐌𝐄 : 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐁𝐮𝐣𝐣𝐢 𝐆𝐚𝐧𝐚𝐩𝐚𝐲𝐲𝐚 𝐉𝐮𝐤𝐞𝐛𝐨𝐱 𝐒𝐨𝐧𝐠𝐬 𝟐𝟎𝟐𝟓

𝐋𝐘𝐑𝐈𝐂𝐒 & 𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂 & 𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐃𝐄𝐕𝐀 𝐑𝐀𝐉𝐔 ~ {𝐏𝐚𝐥𝐚𝐦𝐮𝐫𝐮}

𝐒𝐈𝐍𝐆𝐄𝐑'𝐒  : 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘 & 𝐑𝐀𝐌𝐀𝐍𝐀

𝐌𝐔𝐒𝐈𝐂𝐈𝐀𝐍𝐒 : 𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐤𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐡 𝐊𝐞𝐲𝐛𝐨𝐚𝐫𝐝
                    𝐏𝐫𝐚𝐬𝐚𝐝 : 𝐓𝐚𝐛𝐥𝐚 & 𝐃𝐡𝐨𝐥𝐚𝐤
                     𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐮 :𝐓𝐚𝐩𝐞𝐬
                     𝐒𝐮𝐫𝐞𝐬𝐡 : 𝐑𝐡𝐲𝐭𝐡𝐦 𝐏𝐚𝐝𝐬
                    𝐒𝐫𝐢𝐧𝐢𝐯𝐚𝐬 : 𝐅𝐥𝐮𝐭𝐞

 𝐏𝐑𝐎𝐃𝐔𝐂𝐄𝐑 : 𝐓𝐍,𝐘𝐄𝐋𝐋𝐀 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜 𝐋𝐚𝐛𝐞𝐥 : 𝐓𝐍𝐘𝐑 𝐌𝐮𝐬𝐢𝐜

𝐒𝐏𝐄𝐂𝐀𝐋 𝐓𝐇𝐀𝐍𝐊𝐒 : 𝐘𝐀𝐃𝐈 𝐌𝐔𝐃𝐈𝐑𝐀𝐉 & 𝐀, 𝐉𝐀𝐍𝐆𝐈 𝐑𝐄𝐃𝐃𝐘

snippet.description:

🎶 सुपरहिट गणपती गाणी | भक्ति गीत | Marathi Ganpati Song

Song Credits:
🎤 Singers: Suryakant Shinde
🎼 Music: Madhu Redkar
🎬 Production: Rohit Kathuria
📀 Label: © Fountain Music Company

gu.title: 🌸 નોનસ્ટોપ ગણેશ ભજનો🌼 ગણેશ ચતુર્થી સ્પેશિયલ ગીતો🎶ટોચના 10 ગણેશ ભજનો
gu.description:
આ ભાવપૂર્ણ ગણેશ ચતુર્થી સ્પેશિયલ ભજન પ્લેલિસ્ટ સાથે ભગવાન ગણેશના દિવ્ય આશીર્વાદની ઉજવણી કરો 🎶🐘. આ શક્તિશાળી ગણેશ ભજન, આરતીઓ અને મંત્રો જીવનમાંથી શાંતિ, સકારાત્મકતા, સમૃદ્ધિ લાવે છે અને તમામ અવરોધો દૂર કરે છે 🌸💫.

🌼 પ્લેલિસ્ટમાં શામેલ છે:
1️⃣ જયદેવ જયદેવ જય મંગલ મૂર્તિ

🌸✨ ગણેશ ભજન સાંભળવાના ફાયદા:
🪔 જીવનમાંથી અવરોધો દૂર કરે છે
🪔 શાંતિ, સમૃદ્ધિ અને સફળતા લાવે છે
🪔 ઘરને સકારાત્મકતા અને દૈવી ઉર્જાથી ભરી દે છે
🪔 ગણેશ ચતુર્થીની ઉજવણી દરમિયાન શ્રદ્ધા મજબૂત કરે છે

🕉️🙏 ચાલો આ ગણેશ ચતુર્થીએ ભગવાન ગણેશની સ્તુતિ કરીને જીવનમાં સુખ, સમૃદ્ધિ અને શાંતિનું સ્વાગત કરીએ. 🌼✨

snippet.title: गणेश चतुर्थी Special |नॉनस्टॉप गणेश भजन Nonstop Ganesh Bhajan |Ganesh Song | Ganesh Chaturthi Bhajan
snippet.description:
गणेश चतुर्थी Special |नॉनस्टॉप गणेश भजन Nonstop Ganesh Bhajan |Ganesh Song | Ganesh Chaturthi Bhajan


तो आईए आज पावन हृदय से इस भजन द्वारा जो मांगना है मांग लीजिए।
श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

गणेश जी के रोज नए नए भजन सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़ें रहे व् नए नए भजनों का आनंद उठाये भजन पसंद आये तो कमेंट में '' जय श्री गणेश " जरुर लिखें || Jai Shree Shyam 🌹🌹

⭐Song : 
गौरी नंदन थारो अभिनंदन 
जल्दी से आओ गणपत
मेरे घर भी पधारो देवा
सबसे पहले तुम्हे मनाऊं 
मेरे लाडले गणेश प्यारे प्यारे
तस्वीर तुम्हारी है
मेरे कीर्तन में रंग बरसाओ 
बल बुद्धि के दाता 
श्री गणेश जी के 108 नाम
सुखकर्ता दुःखहर्ता आरती
⭐Singer : 
⭐Lyrics : Traditional
⭐Music: Binny Narang (9991980610)
⭐Video: Shalini Sharma (7015960610)
⭐Label Bhakti Sadhna (9466651081)
⭐Category: Hindi Devotional (Shyam Bhajan)
भक्ति साधना कंपनी से भजन बनवाने के लिए और भजन रिलीज़ करवाने के लिए संपर्क करे 9466651081

श्याम बाबा सबकी मनोकामनांए पूर्ण करें। 🙏

गणेश जी के रोज नए नए भजन सुनने के लिए हमारे साथ जुड़ें रहे व् नए नए भजनों का आनंद उठाये भजन पसंद आये तो कमेंट में '' जय श्री गणेश " जरुर लिखें || Jai Shree Shyam 🌹🌹

गौरी नंदन थारो अभिनंदन 
जल्दी से आओ गणपत
मेरे घर भी पधारो देवा
सबसे पहले तुम्हे मनाऊं 
मेरे लाडले गणेश प्यारे प्यारे
तस्वीर तुम्हारी है
मेरे कीर्तन में रंग बरसाओ 
बल बुद्धि के दाता 
श्री गणेश जी के 108 नाम
सुखकर्ता दुःखहर्ता आरती

⭐Lyrics : Traditional

snippet.title: SISU: Road to Revenge - Official Trailer (HD)
snippet.description:
Vengeance has a name. Watch the official trailer for #SISU: Road to Revenge - exclusively in movie theatres November 21.

Visit our site: http://sisuroadtorevenge.movie/

Follow us on social:
https://www.instagram.com/sisumovie
https://www.tiktok.com/@sisumovieofficial
https://www.facebook.com/sisumovieoffical/
https://twitter.com/sisumovie

Subscribe for more exclusive content: @sonypictures 

SISU: ROAD TO REVENGE is a wall-to-wall cinematic action event, a sequel to the original sleeper hit SISU. Returning to the house where his family was brutally murdered during the war, “the man who refuses to die” (Jorma Tommila) dismantles it, loads it on a truck, and is determined to rebuild it somewhere safe in their honor. When the Red Army commander who killed his family (Stephen Lang from Don’t Breathe) comes back hellbent on finishing the job, a relentless, eye-popping cross-country chase ensues - a fight to the death, full of clever, unbelievable action set pieces.

Directed by: Jalmari Helander

Written by: Jalmari Helander

Produced by: 
Mike Goodridge 
Petri Jokiranta

Executive Producers:
Gregory Ouanhon
Antonio Salas

Cast:
Jorma Tommila
Richard Brake
and Stephen Lang

snippet.title: Mana ShankaraVaraprasad Garu New Trailer' | Megastar Chiranjeevi | Nayanthara | Anil Ravipudi
snippet.description:
Mana ShankaraVaraprasad Garu New Trailer' | Megastar Chiranjeevi | Nayanthara | Anil Ravipudi

#newmovietrailer #anilravipudimovie #newmovie 

About SHINE HUNT :
* On our channel we create а trailer teaser *
Also known as recut trailers, involve collecting multiple pieces of film footage from one or multiple movies A New And Fresh Story, editing them to create a new trailer. Trailer teaser Glimpse are often created for a movie that does not exist now or to change the genre of an existing film..
The trailer mashups are not only a user generated form of digital creativity but a way to create anticipation for future releases, working in tandem with current movie trailers. Movie trailers are designed to give minimal plot detail and to create hype and anticipation. Fan made trailer mashups allow the audience to perform their own cinematic spin on current movie footage. This allows the trailer to focus on a specific actor or portion of the film. snippet.title: Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
The survival action series "Alice in Borderland" became the most watched Japanese Netflix title by worldwide audiences.

Now, the "games" that took the world by storm begin once again.

In the previous season, Arisu (#KentoYamazaki) and Usagi (#TaoTsuchiya) cleared all of the games and returned to the real world. They have since gotten married and established a happy life together. Their memories of the borderland were erased, but they see glimpses of it in dreams and hallucinations. One day, Usagi, led by afterlife researcher Ryuji (#KentoKaku), suddenly vanishes. At the same time as Usagi's disappearance, Banda (#HayatoIsomura) hands Arisu the final card: the Joker.

The uncharted journey led by the mysterious Joker card is about to unfold...

Season 3 of the Netflix Series "Alice in Borderland" is set for worldwide release on Thursday, September 25, 2025, only on Netflix.

#AliceinBorderlandS3, #AliceinBorderland3, #Netflix

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/81682895

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

Alice In Borderland Season 3 | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

When a morbid professor pulls Usagi back to Borderland, Arisu goes after her. But can he survive a new round of deadly games and escape the Joker's plans?

Baget Jate Durva Phul Aanite 
फुल मी आणिते गणपतीला वाहते 
Phul Mi Aanite Ganpatila Vahate 
फुल मी आणिते माझ्या बाप्पाला वाहते
Phul Mi Aanite Majhya Bappala  Vahate

Tujhya Aavadiche Modak Tula Khayala Dete 
खायाला देते तुझं दर्शन घेते
Khayala Dete Tujh Darshan Ghete 
खायाला देते देवाचं दर्शन घेते 
Khayala Dete Devach Darshan Ghete

Hirya Motyachi Kanthi Aanaya Bajara Jate

Kanthi Gheun Yete Bappachya Galyat Ghalate

Aarti Karite Bappacha Modak Dete

snippet.title: Do You Wanna Partner - Official Trailer | Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty | Prime Video India
snippet.description:
Prime Video India Presents
Do You Wanna Partner Official Trailer
Starring Tamannaah Bhatia, Diana Penty, Jaaved Jaaferi, Nakuul Mehta, Neeraj Kabi, Shweta Tiwari, Sufi Motiwala, Rannjivay Singha, Lokesh Mittal, Indranil Sengupta, Ayesha Raza
Directed by Archit Kumar and Collin D'Cunha
Written by Nandini Gupta, Aarsh Vora and Mithun Gangopadhyay
Created by Mithun Gangopadhyay and Nishant Nayak
A Dharmatic Entertainment Production

Official Release Date September 12, 2025 on Prime Video India.

About:
Best friends Shikha and Anahita turn entrepreneurs with an exciting craft beer brand, Jugaaro, to stand out in the crowded NCR beer market. However, they face gender discrimination every step of the way. To fight for an equal place in this male dominated sector, they decide to invent a fictitious male partner to help smooth their way. Invariably, things don’t go exactly as planned. What follows are their collective adventures & misadventures in trying to build a successful start-up amidst the current boom, as the bunch of misfits band together and become a family.

Follow us on:
Instagram: https://www.instagram.com/primevideoin/
Facebook: https://www.facebook.com/PrimeVideoIN/
X: https://x.com/PrimeVideoIN

ABOUT PRIME VIDEO
Prime Video is a one-stop entertainment destination offering customers a vast collection of premium programming in one application available across several devices. On Prime Video, customers can find their favourite Indian and international original series, movies, TV shows, and more, across multiple languages – including Indian-produced Original series like Mirzapur, Farzi, Panchayat, The Family Man, Dhootha, Jubilee, Dahaad, Made in Heaven, Suzhal – The Vortex, Inspector Rishi, Poacher, Indian Police Force, Paatal Lok, Rainbow Rishta, Wedding.con; Original movies like Maja Ma, Ammu, Mast Mein Rehne Ka; popular global Originals like Citadel, The Lord of The Rings: The Rings of Power, Fallout, Reacher, The Boys, The Wheel of Time, Road House, The Idea of You; some of the biggest post-theatrical films; direct-to-service films such as Shershaah, Soorarai Pottru, Sardar Udham, Bawaal, Gehraiyaan, Jai Bhim, Jalsa, Sherni, Narappa, Sarpatta Parambarai, Kuruthi, Joji, Malik, Pippa, HOME, Sharmajee Ki Beti, and many more of such titles. Additionally, Prime Video’s video entertainment marketplace, offers customers programming from partners such as Lionsgate Play, Discovery+ Crunchyroll, BBC Player, Sony Pictures – Stream, MGM+, FanCode, Chaupal, Manorama Max, Eros Now, Hoichoi, Anime Times, to name a few, via Prime Video add-on-subscriptions, as well as the option to rent movies, regardless of whether customers have a Prime membership or not. Customers can also go behind the scenes of their favorite movies and series with exclusive X-Ray access. Prime Video is one benefit among many that provides savings, convenience, and entertainment as part of the Prime membership. For more info visit www.amazon.com/primevideo.

snippet.title: Onbathu Kolum & Vinayagar Songs | ஒன்பது கோளும் & சிறந்த விநாயகர் பாடல்கள் | Vinayaka Chaturthi 2025
snippet.description:
🙏✨ விநாயக சதுர்த்தி 2025 சிறப்பாகக் கொண்டாட, இனிய விநாயகர் பக்திப் பாடல்கள் தொகுப்பு இங்கே. இந்த ஜூக் பாக்ஸில் ஒன்பது கோளும், ஓங்காரமே, மூன்று தமிழ், புனிதம் புனிதம், அருகம்புல்லில், நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன், மற்றும் ஜெய கணேசா போன்ற பிரபலமான பாடல்கள் இடம்பெற்றுள்ளன. பூஜை, விழா மற்றும் பக்தி நேரங்களுக்கு சிறந்த தொகுப்பு.

🎶 பாடல்கள் மற்றும் நேரங்கள்:
00:00 – ஒன்பது கோளும் | Onbathu Kolum
13:07 – ஓங்காரமே | Ongarame
17:49 – மூன்று தமிழ் வாங்க | Moondru Thamizh
23:07 – புனிதம் அரசமரம் | Punitham Punitham
27:36 – அருகம்புல்லில் இருப்பது யாரு | Arugampullil
47:40 – நெற்றியிலே குட்டிக்கொண்டேன் | Nettriyile Kuttikkonden
52:58 – ஜெய கணேச பாஹிமாம் | Jaya Ganesa

🌺 இந்த சதுர்த்தியில் விநாயகர் அருள் உங்கள் குடும்பத்திற்கு மகிழ்ச்சி, ஆரோக்கியம் மற்றும் செழிப்பை வழங்கட்டும்.
👉 மேலும் பல பக்திப் பாடல்களுக்காக Like, Share, Subscribe செய்யுங்கள்.

🙏✨ Celebrate Vinayaka Chaturthi 2025 with a divine collection of powerful Ganesha devotional songs. This special jukebox features evergreen Tamil Vinayagar songs including Onbathu Kolum, Ongarame, Moondru Thamizh, Punitham Punitham, Arugampullil, Nettriyile Kuttikkonden, and Jaya Ganesa. Perfect for Pooja, Festive Celebrations, and Bhakti moments.

🎶 Songs in this Jukebox with Timings:
0:00 – Onbathu Kolum | ஒன்பது கோளும்
13:07 – Ongarame | ஓங்காரமே

snippet.title: DEEWANIYAT - Title Track | Ek Deewane Ki Deewaniyat | Harshvardhan Rane, Sonam Bajwa | Vishal Mishra
snippet.description:
EXPERIENCE THE MADNESS OF LOVE, WHERE PASSION TURNS INTO “DEEWANIYAT”.

THE MOST AWAITED TITLE TRACK “DEEWANIYAT” FROM “EK DEEWANE KI DEEWANIYAT” IS HERE!

A DESI MOVIES FACTORY PRODUCTION

Special Thanks: Virgin Music India

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria


Lyrics :- 
Tere dil pe haq mera hai
Tu sanam beshaq mera
Phir lakeerein hon ya na ho
Tu mera hai tu mera hai

Jo tu aag hai
Haan to phir mujhe
Jalne ka shauk hai
Jalne ka shauk hai
Marne se kahin
Jyada haan tujhe
Khone ka khauf hai
Khone ka khauf hai

Tu chahiye mujhe
Chahe kahe ise 
Mera junu ya phir 
Tu zid meri


Tu hi armaa tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi diwaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe likh chuka hoon
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi ki
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai 
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera


Paane ki tujhko
Hasrat liye hi
Raaton ko main
Jagta hoon
Kyu jaane phir bhi
Dushaman teri do
Ankhon ko 
Main lagta hoon
Kahe na chahe tu mujhe
Karunga tujhe ishq main
Mujhe ye parwaah nahi 
Jo bhi ho mera anjaam har haal mein
Tu chahiye mujhe
Jo bhi saza mile 
Parwaah hai phir kise
Anjaam ki 
Tu hi armaa tu hi sach hai
Keh rahi diwaniyat hai
Main ye dil pe 
Likh chuka hu
Tu mera hai tu mera hai
Tere aage zindagi
Khaakh jitni ehmiyat hai
Faisla main kar chuka hoon
Tu mera main bhi hu bas tera

Lyrics : Gujarati 

હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ...(૨)
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે સૂંઢાળા 
હો અવસર આવીને સુધારો
કે સમરું સ્વામી  તમને સૂંઢાળા 
હો ગરવા ગજાનંદ દેવ છો દયાળા 
મૂષક સવારીએ આવજો ઉતાવળા...(૨)
હે રિદ્ધિ સિદ્ધિ ના સ્વામી પધારો
કે સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા
હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા ...(૨)

હો શેરી સજાવશું સ્વાગતમ્ લખાવુ
હૈયા ના હેતે બાપા તમને વધાવુ 
હો મહેકતા ફૂલડાં મારગે વેરાવુ 
સીમ સીમાડે બાપા સામૈયા કરાવુ  
હો ગરવા ગજાનંદ ગુણ ના ભર્યા
રાખજો બાપા ભયા ધન ના ભંડાર...(૨)
એક દંતા આશરો અમને તમારો 
સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા
હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા...(૨)

હો શિવ શંકર ને માતા પાર્વતી ના પ્યારા
ગણપતિ બાપા આખા જગ થી ન્યારા 
હો આંગણે બાપા પગલા કરજો તમારા
દર્શન દઈ ને જીવન સુધારો અમારા 
હો શુભ લાભ સાથે કરુ પૂજન તમારુ 
કરજો બાપા સપનું પૂરું સપનુ અમારુ...(૨) 
હે અરજી આટલી હાભલો અમારી
કે સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા 
હે ગરવા પાટે  પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા...(૨)

હો અવસર આવીને સુધારો
કે સમરું સ્વામી  તમને સૂંઢાળા 
હો ગરવા ગજાનંદ દેવ છો દયાળા 
મૂષક સવારીએ આવજો ઉતાવળા...(૨)
હે રિદ્ધિ સિદ્ધિ ના સ્વામી પધારો
કે સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા
હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા ...(૨)

હો શેરી સજાવશું સ્વાગતમ્ લખાવુ
હૈયા ના હેતે બાપા તમને વધાવુ 
હો મહેકતા ફૂલડાં મારગે વેરાવુ 
સીમ સીમાડે બાપા સામૈયા કરાવુ  
હો ગરવા ગજાનંદ ગુણ ના ભર્યા
રાખજો બાપા ભયા ધન ના ભંડાર...(૨)
એક દંતા આશરો અમને તમારો 
સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા
હે ગરવા પાટે પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા...(૨)

હો શિવ શંકર ને માતા પાર્વતી ના પ્યારા
ગણપતિ બાપા આખા જગ થી ન્યારા 
હો આંગણે બાપા પગલા કરજો તમારા
દર્શન દઈ ને જીવન સુધારો અમારા 
હો શુભ લાભ સાથે કરુ પૂજન તમારુ 
કરજો બાપા સપનું પૂરું સપનુ અમારુ...(૨) 
હે અરજી આટલી હાભલો અમારી
કે સમરું સ્વામી તમને સૂંઢાળા 
હે ગરવા પાટે  પધારો ગણપતિ 
સુખદાતા દેવ તમે દુંદાળા...(૨)

snippet.title: Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam | Ganesh Chaturthi Special | Vinayaka Chavithi Songs
snippet.description:
🙏 Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha & Pooja Vidhanam – A divine and sacred guide to performing Vinayaka Chavithi Vratham with proper rituals, mantras, and the traditional story of Lord Ganesha.

Narrated by : Tadala Srinivas, I. Muralidhara Sharma


Celebrate this Ganesh Chaturthi with devotion and learn the correct pooja procedure (Vidhanam) along with the auspicious Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu. This video is perfect for those who wish to observe the vratam at home with sincerity and faith.

Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha is a central part of the Vinayaka Vratham Telugu tradition, observed with deep devotion during VinayakaChavithi. On this auspicious day, devotees perform the Vinayaka Pooja Vidhanam Telugu, carefully following each of the Vinayaka Pooja Steps as outlined in the Ganesh Chaturthi Pooja Procedure.

The atmosphere is filled with devotion as families come together, guided by the Vinayaka Vratha Pooja Guide, to offer prayers and perform rituals. The celebration is further enhanced by spiritual music, including Vinayaka Chavithi Songs, Ganesh Chaturthi Special Songs, and uplifting Lord Ganesha Devotional Songs.

Songs like Vinayaka Aarti Telugu, Ganesh Bhakti Songs Telugu, and the latest Vinayaka Chavithi 2025 Telugu Songs add a divine rhythm to the puja. This GaneshChaturthiSpecial becomes even more meaningful when observed with heartfelt devotion, traditional GaneshChaturthiPooja, and the blessings of Lord Ganesha.

🌿 Highlights:
✔ Complete Vinayaka Chavithi Pooja Vidhanam
✔ Sri Vinayaka Vratha Kadha in Telugu
✔ Ideal for Ganesh Chaturthi festival celebrations

✨ Chant, pray, and invite Lord Vinayaka’s blessings for prosperity, wisdom, and happiness.

📌 Don’t forget to Like, Share, and Subscribe for more devotional content, songs, and pooja guides.

snippet.title: नथुनिया 2 | Nathuniya 2 | Lyrical | Khesari Lal New Song | Daisy Shah | Bhojpuri Song | भोजपुरी गाना
snippet.description:
नथुनिया 2 का नया लिरिकल वीडियो खेसारी लाल यादव और डेज़ी शाह की दमदार जोड़ी के साथ भोजपुरिया अंदाज़ में रिलीज़ हो गया है।

Subscribe to our channel for more Bhojpuri Songs:
https://youtube.com/c/SaregamaHumBhojpuri

Credits:-

Song – Nathuniya 2 
Singer – Khesari Lal Yadav
Featuring – Daisy Shah
Lyrics & Music – Krishna Bedardi 
Composer – KRK Yadav
Music Arranger – VS Chauhan
Director - Sumit Kumar & Rohit Shetty
Choreographer - Rohit Shetty 
DOP - Jason Nambardar
Editor - Nitin FCP
Asst. Director - Pawan Pandey
Asst. Editor - Narendra Jaiswal
2nd Asst. Editor - Siddharth Tiwari
Post Production - Arts For Production 
Colorist - Tapasvi Asija
Video by - Sushil Pandey (ZQE Pictures)
Production House: Siddhivinayak Media

Lyrics:-

हो अपना अखियां में काजरा लगाके,
रखनी जुड़ा में साड़ी अटकाके,,
आ हमार पावडर क्रीम लागे हो जाई डिम बाटे एकही जगहिया खाली,,
हो सईया बिन नथुनिया के डाली,,

त चोली चिल्लाता ये राजा हो जल्दी आ जा हो,
कमर से साड़ी सरक जाता सीरिया जा हो,,
त करी अईसन सिंगार के 
बिन भतार के,
मन नाही करे रही झार के बिन भतार के,,
त कहे बिंदिया बलम तू सतावल कर कम लाल भईल बा घुसा से ओठलाली हो सईया बिन,,,

चूड़ी के शोर सखि भावे ना केहू बजावे ना,
सुना संगीत बा जवानी के केहू गावे ना,,
अब त लागे की कटी ना सर्दी ये बेदर्दी,
इ जवानी खेसारी के नामे मन करे करदी,,
रहिते घरे बलम होईत गाना गरम 
ओ में कबो कबो होईत कऊवाली ,, हो सइया बिन,,

Ho apna akhiyan mein kajra lagake
Rakhni juda mein saadi takaake
Ho apna akhiyan mein kajra lagake
Rakhni juda mein saadi takaake
Aa hamar powder cream laage ho jaayi dim
Baate ekahi jagahiya khaali

Ho saiyan bin nathuniya....
Ho saiyan bin nathuniya ke daali
Ho raja bin nathuniya ke daali

Ta choli chillata ye raja ho, jaldi aa ja ho
Kamar se saadi sarak jaata seeriya ja ho
Ta kari aisan singaar ke
Bin bhatar ke

Man naahi kare rahi jhaar ke, bin bhatar ke
Ta kahe bindiya Balam tu satawal kar
Kam laal bhail ba ghussa se othalali
Ho saiyan bin nathuniya......
Ho saiyan bin nathuniya ke daali
Ho raja bin nathuniya ke daali

Chudi ke shor sakhi bhawe na, kehu bajawe na
Suna sangeet ba jawani ke, kehu gawe na
Ab ta laage ki kati na sardi ye bedardi
Ee jawani Khesari ke naame man kare kardi
Rahite ghare Balam hoit gaana garam
O mein kabho kabho hoit kauwaali, 
Ho saiyan bin nathuniya......
Ho saiyan bin nathuniya ke daali
Ho raja bin nathuniya ke daali.

#khesarilalyadav 
#khesari 
#daisyshah 
#saregamahumbhojpuri 
#bhojpuri 
#bhojpurimusic 
#bhojpurisong
